#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.72"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.72:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.72:0.2"
msgid "8. Yodhājīvavagga"
msgstr "8. Warriors"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.72:0.3"
msgid "72. Dutiyacetovimuttiphalasutta"
msgstr "72. Freedom of Heart is the Fruit (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.72:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcime, bhikkhave, dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā cetovimuttiphalā ca honti "
"cetovimuttiphalānisaṃsā ca, paññāvimuttiphalā ca honti "
"paññāvimuttiphalānisaṃsā ca."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, these five things, when developed and cultivated, have freedom "
"of heart and freedom by wisdom as their fruit and benefit."

msgctxt "an5.72:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.72:1.3"
msgid ""
"Aniccasaññā, anicce dukkhasaññā, dukkhe anattasaññā, pahānasaññā, "
"virāgasaññā—"
msgstr ""
"The perception of impermanence, the perception of suffering in impermanence, "
"the perception of not-self in suffering, the perception of giving up, and "
"the perception of fading away."

msgctxt "an5.72:1.4"
msgid ""
"ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā cetovimuttiphalā ca "
"honti cetovimuttiphalānisaṃsā ca, paññāvimuttiphalā ca honti "
"paññāvimuttiphalānisaṃsā ca."
msgstr ""
"These five things, when developed and cultivated, have freedom of heart and "
"freedom by wisdom as their fruit and benefit."

msgctxt "an5.72:1.5"
msgid "Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cetovimutto ca hoti paññāvimutto ca—"
msgstr "When a mendicant has freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom,"

msgctxt "an5.72:1.6"
msgid ""
"ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, ‘bhikkhu ukkhittapaligho itipi, saṅkiṇṇaparikho "
"itipi, abbūḷhesiko itipi, niraggaḷo itipi, ariyo pannaddhajo pannabhāro "
"visaṃyutto itipi’”."
msgstr ""
"they’re called a mendicant who has lifted up the cross-bar, filled in the "
"trench, and pulled up the pillar; they’re unbarred, a noble one with banner "
"and burden put down, detached. …”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.72:2.1"
msgid "“Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ukkhittapaligho hoti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.72:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno avijjā pahīnā hoti ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā "
"anabhāvaṅkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.72:2.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ukkhittapaligho hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.86"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.72:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saṅkiṇṇaparikho hoti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.72:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno ponobhaviko jātisaṃsāro pahīno hoti ucchinnamūlo "
"tālāvatthukato anabhāvaṅkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.72:3.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saṅkiṇṇaparikho hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.72:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu abbūḷhesiko hoti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.72:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno taṇhā pahīnā hoti ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā "
"anabhāvaṅkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.72:4.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu abbūḷhesiko hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.72:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu niraggaḷo hoti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.72:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pañcorambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni pahīnāni honti "
"ucchinnamūlāni tālāvatthukatāni anabhāvaṅkatāni āyatiṃ anuppādadhammāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.72:5.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu niraggaḷo hoti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.72:6.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyo pannaddhajo pannabhāro visaṃyutto hoti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.72:6.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno asmimāno pahīno hoti ucchinnamūlo tālāvatthukato "
"anabhāvaṅkato āyatiṃ anuppādadhammo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.72:6.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyo pannaddhajo pannabhāro visaṃyutto hotī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.72:6.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
